ese%20hackers%20have%20been%20using%20AI%20tools%20to%20supercharge%20espionage%20and%20slip%20into%20companies%20and%20other%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20latest%20case%2C%20a%20North%20Korean%20hacking%20group%20known%20as%20Kimusky%20used%20ChatGPT%20to%20generate%20a%20fake%20draft%20of%20a%20South%20Korean%20military%20ID.%20The%20fake%20IDs%20were%20attached%20to%20phishing%20emails%20that%20impersonated%20a%20South%20Korean%20defense%20institution%20responsible%20for%20issuing%20credentials%20to%20military-affiliated%20officials%2C%20South%20Korean%20cybersecurity%20firm%20Genians%20said%20in%20a%20blog%20post%20published%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKimsuky%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20a%20string%20of%20espionage%20campaigns%20against%20individuals%20and%20organizations%20in%20South%20Korea%2C%20Japan%2C%20and%20the%20US.%20In%202020%2C%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20said%20the%20group%20is%20%26quot%3Bmost%20likely%20tasked%20by%20the%20North%20Korean%20regime%20with%20a%20global%20intelligence-gathering%20mission.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChatGPT%20blocks%20attempts%20to%20generate%20official%20government%20IDs.%20But%20the%20model%20could%20be%20coaxed%20into%20producing%20convincing%20mock-ups%20if%20the%20prompt%20was%20framed%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsample%20design%20for%20legitimate%20purposes%20rather%20than%20reproducing%20an%20actual%20military%20ID%2C%26quot%3B%20Genians%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20North%20Korean%20hackers%20have%20used%20AI%20to%20infiltrate%20foreign%20entities.%20Anthropic%20said%20in%20a%20report%20last%20month%20that%20North%20Korean%20hackers%20used%20its%20Claude%20tool%20to%20secure%20and%20maintain%20fraudulent%20remote%20employment%20at%20American%20Fortune%20500%20tech%20companies.%20The%20hackers%20used%20Claude%20to%20spin%20up%20convincing%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20portfolios%2C%20pass%20coding%20tests%2C%20and%20even%20complete%20real%20technical%20assignments%20once%20they%20were%20on%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20officials%20said%20last%20year%20that%20North%20Korea%20was%20placing%20people%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-helped-north-korea-find-remote-jobs-in-us-prosecutors-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eremote%20positions%20in%20US%20firms%3C%2Fa%3E%20using%20false%20or%20stolen%20identities%20as%20part%20of%20a%20mass%20extortion%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4ada8fd-dc97-4674-a619-878d9e6d0f6f%5C%22%3EChina's%20hackers%20are%20doing%20it%2C%20too%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20said%20in%20the%20same%20report%20that%20a%20Chinese%20actor%20spent%20over%20nine%20months%20using%20Claude%20as%20a%20full-stack%20cyberattack%20assistant%20to%20target%20major%20Vietnamese%20telecommunications%20providers%2C%20agricultural%20systems%2C%20and%20government%20databases.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hacker%20used%20Claude%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btechnical%20advisor%2C%20code%20developer%2C%20security%20analyst%2C%20and%20operational%20consultant%20throughout%20their%20campaign%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthropic%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnthropic%20said%20it%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-agentic-ai-vibe-hacking-weaponized-cyberattack-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimplemented%20new%20ways%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20detect%20misuse%20of%20its%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20hackers%20have%20also%20been%20turning%20to%20ChatGPT%20for%20help%20with%20their%20cyber%20campaigns%2C%20according%20to%20an%20OpenAI%20report%20published%20in%20June.%20The%20hackers%20asked%20the%20chatbot%20to%20generate%20code%20for%20%26quot%3Bpassword%20bruteforcing%26quot%3B%E2%80%94%20scripts%20that%20guess%20thousands%20of%20username%20and%20password%20combinations%20until%20one%20works.%20They%20used%20ChatGPT%20to%20dig%20up%20information%20on%20US%20defense%20networks%2C%20satellite%20systems%2C%20and%20government%20ID%20verification%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20OpenAI%20report%20flagged%20a%20China-based%20influence%20operation%20that%20used%20ChatGPT%20to%20generate%20social%20media%20posts%20designed%20to%20stoke%20division%20in%20US%20politics%2C%20including%20fake%20profile%20images%20to%20make%20the%20accounts%20look%20like%20real%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20operation%20we%20disrupt%20gives%20us%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20how%20threat%20actors%20are%20trying%20to%20abuse%20our%20models%2C%20and%20enables%20us%20to%20refine%20our%20defenses%2C%26quot%3B%20OpenAI%20said%20in%20the%20June%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Claude%20and%20ChatGPT.%20North%20Korean%20and%20Chinese%20hackers%20have%20experimented%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhackers-google-ai-chatbot-gemini-cyberattacks-china-iran-north-korea-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle's%20Gemini%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20expand%20their%20operations.%20Chinese%20groups%20used%20the%20chatbot%20to%20troubleshoot%20code%20and%20obtain%20%26quot%3Bdeeper%20access%20to%20target%20networks%2C%26quot%3B%20while%20North%20Korean%20actors%20used%20Gemini%20to%20draft%20fake%20cover%20letters%20and%20scout%20IT%20job%20postings%2C%20Google%20said%20in%20a%20January%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20said%20Gemini's%20safeguards%20prevented%20hackers%20from%20using%20it%20for%20more%20sophisticated%20attacks%2C%20such%20as%20accessing%20information%20to%20manipulate%20Google's%20own%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenAI%2C%20Anthropic%2C%20and%20Google%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%20The%20companies%20have%20said%20they%20published%20their%20findings%20on%20hackers%20to%20help%20others%20improve%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295fbcd90-5507-4ac7-a7f5-b1cdc88579bd%5C%22%3EAI%20makes%20hacking%20easier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECybersecurity%20experts%20have%20long%20warned%20that%20AI%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20make%20hacking%20and%20disinformation%20operations%20easier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHackers%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-hackers-models-hugging-face-opensource-jfrog-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eusing%20AI%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20infiltrate%20companies%2C%20Yuval%20Fernbach%2C%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20of%20machine%20learning%20operations%20at%20software%20supply%20chain%20company%20JFrog%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20report%20published%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20seeing%20many%2C%20many%20attacks%2C%26quot%3B%20Fernbach%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20malicious%20code%20is%20easily%20hidden%20inside%20open-source%20large%20language%20models.%20Hackers%20typically%20shut%20things%20down%2C%20steal%20information%2C%20or%20change%20the%20output%20of%20a%20website%20or%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerica-small-business-owners-swamped-by-scammers-generative-ai-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOnline%20businesses%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20also%20been%20hit%20by%20deepfakes%20and%20scams.%20Rob%20Duncan%2C%20the%20VP%20of%20strategy%20at%20the%20cybersecurity%20firm%20Netcraft%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20June%20report%20that%20he%20isn't%20surprised%20at%20the%20surge%20in%20personalized%20phishing%20attacks%20against%20small%20businesses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenAI%20tools%20now%20allow%20even%20a%20novice%20lone%20wolf%20with%20little%20technical%20know-how%20to%20clone%20a%20brand's%20image%20and%20write%20flawless%2C%20convincing%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbank-account-scam-deepfakes-ai-voice-generator-crime-fraud-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escam%20messages%3C%2Fa%3E%20within%20minutes%2C%20Duncan%20said.%20With%20cheap%20tools%2C%20%26quot%3Battackers%20can%20more%20easily%20spoof%20employees%2C%20fool%20customers%2C%20or%20impersonate%20partners%20across%