a.%20Inside%2C%20two%20serious-looking%20staffers%20dressed%20in%20black%20greeted%20me.%20They%20declined%20to%20be%20named%20or%20say%20how%20many%20people%20work%20at%20Kuma.%20They%20told%20me%20I%20couldn't%20photograph%20instructors'%20or%20participants'%20faces%20without%20their%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20received%20malicious%20emails%20from%20trolls%2C%20unidentified%20parcels%20in%20the%20mail%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20staffer%20told%20me%2C%20declining%20to%20reveal%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20founder%20has%20received%20threats%20that%20they'll%20make%20his%20daughter%20an%20orphan%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20staffer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20the%20first%20impression%20it%20gives%20off%2C%20this%20is%20no%20hardcore%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdefense%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emilitary%20school%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20a%20nonprofit%20that%20tries%20to%20prepare%20civilians%20for%20the%20scenario%20no%20one%20wants%20to%20be%20in%3A%20What%20happens%20if%20China%20invades%20Taiwan%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22655d11ee-5b6c-465b-a595-63089b745217%5C%22%3ETraining%20for%20a%20Chinese%20invasion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20China%20escalates%20military%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fchina%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epolitical%20pressure%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20thousands%20of%20Taiwanese%20civilians%20are%20quietly%20preparing%20for%20a%20war%20they%20hope%20never%20comes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFounded%20in%202021%2C%20Kuma%20Academy%20is%20one%20of%20Taiwan's%20most%20prominent%20civilian%20defense%20nonprofits%20and%20a%20key%20player%20in%20its%20grassroots%20preparedness%20movement.%20It's%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20network%20that%20offers%20everything%20from%20first%20aid%20and%20disinformation%20resilience%20to%20evacuation%20and%20digital%20security%20planning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKuma%20says%20it%20has%20trained%20around%2080%2C000%20people%2C%20mostly%20aged%2025%20to%2045.%20About%2070%25%20of%20its%20trainees%20are%20women%20%E2%80%94%20a%20stark%20contrast%20to%20Taiwan's%20traditional%20civil%20defense%20units%2C%20which%20skew%20heavily%20male%20and%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20mostly%20elderly%20male%20citizens%20within%20that%20group%20%E2%80%94%20so%20it%20only%20retains%20the%20purpose%20of%20socializing%2C%20which%20defeats%20the%20original%20purpose%20of%20defense%20training%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20Kuma%20Academy%20employee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20branding%20is%20%E2%80%94%20there's%20no%20other%20way%20to%20put%20it%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Ecute.%20%3C%2Fem%3EIts%20logo%20features%20a%20black%20cartoon%20bear%20holding%20a%20rifle%2C%20and%20its%20merch%20is%20decked%20out%20with%20the%20same%20bear%20and%20other%20woodland%20creatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kuma%20Academy%20merchandise.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c1322d57d362d375e7de1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EKuma%20Academy%20merchandise%20features%20a%20playful%2C%20cute%20aesthetic.%3Cp%3EHuileng%20Tan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKuma%20runs%20several%20courses.%20The%20one-day%20workshop%20I%20attended%20cost%20about%201%2C200%20Taiwan%20dollars%2C%20or%20about%20%2440.%20As%20a%20member%20of%20the%20press%2C%20I%20was%20there%20to%20observe%2C%20not%20participate%2C%20and%20I%20was%20given%20free%20access%20to%20the%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInside%20the%20classroom%2C%20the%20tone%20was%20instructional%20rather%20than%20commanding.%20The%20topic%20of%20China%20came%20up%20mostly%20during%20a%20session%20on%20how%20fake%20news%20spreads%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echat%20apps.%3C%2Fa%3E%20The%20instructors%20were%20serious%20but%20measured%2C%20and%20participants%20m