es%20for%20supplying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20emphasize%20enough%20the%20damage%20that%20social%20media%20and%20the%20internet%20is%20doing%20to%20all%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Cox%20said.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20most%20powerful%20companies%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20world%20have%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20hack%20our%20brains%2C%20get%20us%20addicted%20to%20outrage%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20the%20same%20type%20of%20dopamine%2C%20the%20same%20chemical%20you%20get%20from%20taking%20fentanyl%20%E2%80%94%20and%20get%20us%20to%20hate%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20seeing%20it%20in%20real%20time%20in%20the%20tragic%20death%20of%20Charlie%20Kirk.%20I'm%20seeing%20it%20in%20every%20corner%20of%20our%20society.%20The%20conflict%20entrepreneurs%20are%20taking%20advantage%20of%20us%2C%20and%20we%20are%20losing%20our%20agency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECox%2C%20a%2050-year-old%20sixth-generation%20Utahn%20who%20became%20governor%20in%202021%2C%20received%20his%20law%20degree%20from%20Washington%20and%20Lee%20University%20in%202001.%20The%20official%20bio%20for%20Cox%2C%20a%20Republican%2C%20describes%20him%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20voice%20on%20protecting%20youth%20from%20the%20harms%20of%20social%20media.%26quot%3B%20Utah%20passed%20two%20laws%20in%202024%20aimed%20at%20protecting%20minors%20on%20social%20media%20platforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20social%20media%20is%20a%20ubiquitous%20part%20of%20life%20for%20people%20of%20all%20ages%2C%20many%20US%20states%20have%20sued%20social%20media%20companies%20like%20Meta%20and%20TikTok%C2%A0to%20stop%20them%20from%20using%20tactics%20legislators%20deem%20exploitative%20to%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstates-sue-meta-allege-facebook-instagram-harm-youth-mental-health-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E33%20US%20states%20sued%20Meta%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20what%20they%20said%20was%20the%20harm%20those%20companies%20are%20causing%20to%20young%20people's%20mental%20health.%20The%20lawsuit%2C%20filed%20in%20a%20California%20federal%20court%2C%20said%20Meta%20intentionally%20designed%20Facebook%20and%20Instagram%20features%20that%20are%20addictive%20to%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Meta%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20the%20company%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisappointed%20that%20instead%20of%20working%20productively%20with%20companies%20across%20the%20industry%20to%20create%20clear%2C%20age-appropriate%20standards%20for%20the%20many%20apps%20teens%20use%2C%20the%20attorneys%20general%20have%20chosen%20this%20path.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%2014%20attorneys%20general%20also%20filed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-lawsuits-mirror-tobacco-purdue-pharma-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elawsuits%20against%20TikTok%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%20the%20app%20misled%20the%20public%20about%20its%20safety%20and%20harmed%20young%20people's%20mental%20health.%20Minnesota%20became%20the%20latest%20state%20to%20sue%20TikTok%20in%20August.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20TikTok%20spokesperson%20told%20NPR%20last%20year%20that%20TikTok%20had%20implemented%20new%20safety%20features%20for%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20provide%20robust%20safeguards%2C%20proactively%20remove%20suspected%20underage%20users%2C%20and%20have%20voluntarily%20launched%20safety%20features%20such%20as%20default%20screentime%20limits%2C%20family%20pairing%2C%20and%20privacy%20by%20default%20for%20minors%20under%2016%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20endeavored%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Attorneys%20General%20for%20over%20two%20years%2C%20and%20it%20is%20incredibly%20disappointing%20they%20have%20taken%20this%20step%20rather%20than%20work%20with%20us%20on%20constructive%20solutions%20to%20industry-wide%20challenges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20interview%2C%20Cox%20said%20Ameri