%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22columbia%20university%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5eea40d53f737015c205c9c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Columbia%20University%20campus%20is%20seen%20on%20May%2021%2C%202020.%3Cp%3ERob%20Kim%2FGetty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211c64e8d-54c1-43c9-83dc-e80e290158e9%5C%22%3ECustom%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20and%20curated%20opportunities%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENguyen%20says%20one%20of%20Ivy%20Link's%20most%20valuable%20offerings%20is%20helping%20students%20land%20highly%20competitive%20internship%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20is%20a%20high-school%20student%20who%20secured%20a%20spot%20in%20a%20biotech%20lab%20that%20usually%20doesn't%20even%20take%20college%20interns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe's%20in%20high%20school%2C%20but%20he's%20operating%20at%20the%20college%20level%20in%20terms%20of%20STEM%20research%2C%26quot%3B%20Nguyen%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20prepped%20him%20as%20if%20he%20were%20going%20into%20a%20job%20interview%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20outperformed%20even%20my%20college%20students.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENguyen%20added%20that%20many%20opportunities%20come%20from%20family%20connections.%20Ivy%20Link%20simply%20shows%20them%20how%20to%20leverage%20those%20relationships%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20families%20are%20very%20well%20connected%2C%26quot%3B%20Nguyen%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20could%20pick%20up%20the%20phone%20and%20call%20a%20nonprofit%20they've%20donated%20to%20%E2%80%94%20they%20just%20need%20direction.%20We%20help%20tie%20everything%20together%20into%20a%20compelling%20narrative%20that%20makes%20sense.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2211fe2876-fcb9-45a2-a886-f00d3b07b0c6%5C%22%3E%2430%2C000%20semester%20programs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENguyen%20said%20that%20exclusive%20semester-away%20programs%20like%20The%20Mountain%20School%2C%20The%20Island%20School%2C%20and%20Alzar%20School%20%E2%80%94%20each%20costing%20around%20%2430%2C000%20or%20more%20per%20term%20%E2%80%94%20have%20become%20increasingly%20popular%20among%20his%20clients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20programs%2C%20which%20emphasize%20leadership%2C%20character%2C%20and%20outdoor%20resilience%2C%20provide%20a%20rugged%20contrast%20to%20the%20typical%20applicant%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20all%20about%20standing%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Nguyen%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20that%20now%20you're%20different%20from%20all%20the%20kids%20in%20New%20York%20City%20who%20apply%20%E2%80%94%20their%20wildest%20thing%20is%20taking%20the%20subway%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20quick%20to%20stress%20that%20such%20programs%20only%20work%20when%20they're%20a%20natural%20extension%20of%20the%20student's%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20push%20it%20unless%20the%20student's%20very%20outdoorsy%20%E2%80%94%20loves%20camping%2C%20loves%20canoeing%2C%26quot%3B%20Nguyen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENguyen%20also%20works%20with%20families%20to%20gain%20admission%20to%20elite%20feeder%20high%20schools%20%E2%80%94%20places%20like%20Horace%20Mann%2C%20Phillips%20Exeter%20Academy%2C%20or%20St.%20Paul's%20%E2%80%94%20which%20come%20with%20their%20own%20prestige%20pipelines%20to%20Ivy%20League%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20part%20of%20a%20long-term%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%20any%20of%20this.%20It's%20a%20luxury.%20But%20some%20families%20are%20willing%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20edge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228cd3131a-b207-4282-b3f7-8c642d27a6cd%5C%22%3EParents%2C%20boundaries%2C%20and%20the%20business%20of%20prestige%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20all%20the%20money%20and%20strategy%20involved%2C%20Nguyen%20insists%20the%20student%20still%20needs%20to%20do%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20on%20the%20treadmill%20%E2%80%94%20they%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Ivy%20Link%20won't%20write%20essays%2C%20fake%20accomplishments%2C%20or%20take%20shortcuts.%20They%20also%20step%20in%20when%20parents%20get%20too%20pushy%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20time%20a%20billionaire%20client%20asked%20if%20Donald%20Trump%20could%20write%20their%20child's%20recommendation.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20them%3A%20that%20doesn't%20help%20if%20he%20doesn't%20know%20your%20kid.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20case%2C%20Nguyen%20said%20he%20saved%20a%20client%20%2423%20million%20by%20advising%20them%20not%20to%20donate%20to%20a%20university.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20child's%20record%20was%20strong%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20got%20in%20anyway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENguyen%20said%20the%20work%20is%20high-touch%20and%20long-term.%20He's%20coached%20one%20student%20from%20private%20school%20admissions%20to%20Yale%20Law.%20%26quot%3BAt%20this%20point%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20left%20is%20matchmaking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20joked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20taboo%2C%20Nguyen%20said%20elite%20prep%20services%20like%20his%20are%20far%20more%20common%20than%20people%20admit.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20an%20open%20secret%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20talks%20about%20it%20%E2%80%94%20but%20everybody%20gets%20help.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20he%20insists%20that%20success%20isn't%20just%20about%20money.%20%26quot%3BPlanning%2C%20support%2C%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20what%20gets%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20no%20different%20from%20hiring%20a%20great%20coach%20or%20the%20right%20trainer.%20The%20most%20successful%20people%20know%20they%20can't%20do%20it%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-ivy-league-prep-ultrawealthy-30k-schools-and-resumes-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A175