-alone-time-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emy%20own%20stuff%20and%20my%20own%20bed%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20that%20same%20son%20had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-letting-kids-sleep-screentime-do-nothing-summer-break-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ean%20impromptu%20sleepover%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20his%20three%20closest%20friends.%20He%20didn't%20have%20a%20sleeping%20bag%2C%20a%20change%20of%20clothes%2C%20or%20a%20toothbrush%2C%20but%20he%20seemed%20happy%20to%20continue%20the%20all-day%20hangout%20they'd%20been%20having%20(and%20which%20lasted%20into%20the%20next%20afternoon).%20It%20was%20a%20low-maintenance%2C%20drama-free%20sleepover%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20good%20reminder%20that%20independence%20doesn't%20always%20look%20like%20pushing%20boundaries.%20Sometimes%20it%20looks%20like%20knowing%20when%20you%20feel%20comfortable%20and%20when%20you%20don't.%20And%20I%20love%20that%20he%20felt%20comfortable%20with%20a%20spontaneous%20sleepover%20just%20as%20much%20as%20I%20love%20that%20he%20feels%20comfortable%20calling%20to%20be%20picked%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241ac081c-904e-4642-88ad-b1950186a432%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20reassuring%20to%20see%20them%20make%20their%20own%20choices%20now%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhelicopter-parenting-could-hurt-kids-2016-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20think%20of%20myself%20as%20a%20helicopter%20parent%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I%20do%20hover.%20Not%20to%20control%20my%20kids%2C%20but%20to%20be%20available.%20To%20reinforce%2C%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%20that%20they%20have%20options%20and%20they%20don't%20have%20to%20go%20along%20with%20the%20crowd.%20That%20they're%20allowed%20to%20trust%20their%20instincts%20and%20change%20their%20minds%20for%20any%20reason.%20I%20want%20them%20to%20practice%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthis%20isn't%20for%20me%26quot%3B%20in%20small%2C%20saf